2023-03-16

library(magick)
top_text <- "old man and R.LOG"
# Read in image
pict1 <- image_read("https://jeroen.github.io/images/frink.png")
pict2<-image_read("https://jeroen.github.io/images/Rlogo-old.png")
pict3<-image_append(c(pict1,pict2))

# Create a background
bg <- image_blank(width = 800, 
                  height = 600,
                  color = "white")%>%
  image_annotate(text = top_text, 
                 size = 50, 
                 color = "black", 
                 gravity = "north")

# Composite the image onto the background
result <- image_composite(bg, pict3, offset = "+100+50")

# Save the result
image_write(result, "my_meme.png")

library(magick)
img_seq <- image_read("https://jeroen.github.io/images/Rlogo.png")
delay_time <- 10
anim_gif <- image_animate(img_seq, delay = delay_time)
image_write(anim_gif, "Rlogo_png.gif")
